item.title: More help with server
item.dc:creator: @Cool_Kiid Cool Kiid
item.description:
@Cool_Kiid wrote:

C:/Program Files (86x)/java/jre6/bin/java

Well. It’s not 86x it’s x86 and it’s java.exe

Use this code- C:/Program Files (x86)/java/jre6/bin/java.exe
